    org.cell2d.space.basic  
  • Classes in org.cell2d.space.basic used by org.cell2d.space.basic 
    Class and Description
    BasicSpaceState
    A BasicSpaceState is a type of SpaceState that uses BasicSpaceThinkers, which have no special capabilities, and treats its CellGame as a basic CellGame.
    BasicSpaceThinker
    A BasicSpaceThinker is a type of SpaceThinker that is used by BasicSpaceStates, which have no special capabilities, and treats their CellGames as basic CellGames.
